#slide[
  = What to do about the Lexer?

  We should aim to complete the grammar by Saturday (2 May, 2026) and the lexer by Monday (4 May, 2026).

  - *Why do we need a grammar?*
    - I want this project to be as educational as it is practical. Learning how the grammars from compiler theory translate to actual lexer/parser code is part of that.
  - *Why these specific dates?*
    - I planned for every component (lexer, parser, codegen, raylib+pong) to take 1 week each. These aren't hard deadlines, they're suggestions. If you'd like to amend them, please speak up!
  - *How do I do [x]?*
    - If you have questions, please google them, ask them in the `#help` channel or in `#contrib` - asking questions quicker will unblock you quicker!
]
